\c 124
\s Murwiri waIsraeri ngaarumbidzwe
\d Rwiyo rworwendo; rwaDhavhidhi
\p
\v 1 Dai Jehovha asaiva nesu, Israeri ngavadaro;
\v 2 dai Jehovha asaiva nesu, panguva yatakamukirwa navanhu;
\v 3 vangadai vakatimedza tiri vapenyu, panguva yatakamukirwa nehasha dzavo.
\v 4 Mvura zhinji ingadai yakatifukidza, rwizi rungadai rwakapfuura napamusoro pomweya wedu.
\v 5 Mvura zhinji, inozvikudza, ingadai yakapfuura napamusoro pomweya wedu.
\p
\v 6 Jehovha ngaarumbidzwe, iye asina kutiisa kuti tiparadzwe nameno avo.
\v 7 Mweya wedu wapukunyuka seshiri parugombe rwomuteyi weshiri; rugombe rwadambuka, isu tapukunyuka.
\v 8 Kubatsirwa kwedu kuri muzita raJehovha, akaita kudenga napasi.
